  "title": "Senior Quantity Surveyor - Jurong East",
  "description": "<p>We are seeking a detail-oriented and experienced <strong>Senior Quantity Surveyor</strong> to join our project team. The ideal candidate will manage the full spectrum of cost and contract administration for <strong>construction, ACMV, and M&amp;E projects</strong>, ensuring value, compliance, and profitability throughout each project’s lifecycle.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<h3><strong>Responsibilities</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>Prepare, review, and manage <strong>cost estimates, budgets, and tender documents</strong> for projects.</li>\n  <li>Evaluate <strong>tender submissions</strong>, negotiate with subcontractors, and make recommendations for award.</li>\n  <li>Conduct <strong>quantity take-offs, cost analysis, and value engineering</strong> to optimize project costs.</li>\n  <li>Prepare and manage <strong>progress claims, variation orders, and final accounts</strong> with clients and subcontractors.</li>\n  <li>Ensure compliance with <strong>contractual terms, drawings, and specifications</strong>.</li>\n  <li>Work closely with Project Managers and Engineers to monitor project cost performance and control expenses.</li>\n  <li>Prepare <strong>cash flow projections</strong> and assist in project financial reporting.</li>\n  <li>Provide advice on <strong>contractual and commercial matters</strong> throughout project execution.</li>\n  <li>Lead and mentor junior QS staff to ensure quality and efficiency in work delivery.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3><strong>Qualifications:</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>Minimum <strong>Diploma or Degree in Quantity Surveying, Building, or related discipline</strong>.</li>\n  <li>At least <strong>5–8 years of relevant experience</strong> in construction / M&amp;E / ACMV projects.</li>\n  <li>Strong knowledge of <strong>contract law, procurement processes, and cost control principles</strong>.</li>\n  <li>Proficient in <strong>MS Office, or other QS software</strong>.</li>\n  <li>Excellent <strong>analytical, negotiation, and communication skills</strong>.</li>\n  <li>Able to work independently and lead a small team effectively.</li>\n</ul>",
